attachments.title: Interactive Game of Thrones Map with Spoilers Control
attachments.text: A map of Westeros and the rest of the known world in Game of Thrones and the Song of Ice & Fire novels. Mark how much of the TV show or novels you've seen to prevent seeing any spoilers. See the path of major characters over time.
attachments.fallback: Interactive Game of Thrones Map with Spoilers Control

text: it’s super awesome! You can track individual characters episode-by-episode or chapter-by-chapter
(just re-watched sunday’s episode. a little slow - but really great plot building)
